Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张间同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.40,0:01:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.63,0:01:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若立誓成为一名出色的池袋人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须得克服这次考验
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了…我的爱
