Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服了 真的服了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错 塞尔堤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我接了无聊的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作本应该顺利解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是当时…偶然出现了那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人 怪物 怪物 怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口处传来声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它说我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它至少该说你是魔女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是外星人该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞尔堤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是笑点么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪…怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.51,0:03:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城市似乎是由玩笑 随性和偶然构成的
