Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:04:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs30}我 所以 渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:04:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs30}我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:04:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\fs30}是渴望强者所以人类是爱\N是是渴望所以所以所以
